title: Ursula K. Le Guin - Earthsea Cycle 1-6 (retail epub, mobi)
description:
Ursula K. Le Guin - The Earthsea Cycle, 6 volumes, all from a retail source. Mobi versions converted from epub source. Includes calibre metadata and high resolution cover images.

1. A Wizard of Earthsea
2. The Tombs of Atuan
3. The Farthest Shore
4. Tehanu
5. Tales from Earthsea
6. The Other Wind

The books in this torrent are good enough quality that they can replace any older versions, which were (at least for volumes 1-3) amateur, ocr-based versions. Some of them were good quality, but these are the best.
